VS : ViganServer << Just what I like to call my developing servers.
Contains:
- Loads 481 cache maps not objects, including: Godwars, Bounty hunter, Clan wars, Barbarian assault, Warriors' guild, Lunar Isle, Neitiznot Isle and more!
- Loads a clean 377 cache - Loads 420 sprites replaced by cache - 474 font - Hint icons (arrow above NPC's head) - Ready for adding models - Ready for adding new interfaces - Perfect starting base

No pictures, sorry.
